{{vgname|X 重生|en=X Rebirth}}是德国游戏开发商[[Egosoft|Egosoft]]开发的一款[[太空模拟游戏|太空模拟游戏]]，是[[X系列_(游戏)|X系列]]游戏的第六作。该游戏于2013年11月15日发布。是《X³：阿尔比恩序曲》后的续作。<ref name="Joystiq-x-rebirth-fletcher-2011-04-22">{{cite news | first = J. C. | last = Fletcher | title = Egosoft's ''X Rebirth'' brings the space exploration series back to life | date = 2011-04-22 | publisher = [[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | url = http://www.joystiq.com/2011/04/22/egosofts-x-rebirth-brings-the-space-exploration-series-back-t/ | work = [[AOL|AOL Inc.]] | accessdate = 2016-12-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110427022730/http://www.joystiq.com/2011/04/22/egosofts-x-rebirth-brings-the-space-exploration-series-back-t | archive-date = 2011-04-27 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>本作运行在Microsoft Windows、Mac OS X、Linux环境下，Egosoft的总监Bernd Lehahn表示《X 重生》不会在游戏机平台运行。<ref name="X Universe 43">{{Cite web |url=http://www.egosoft.com/x/xnews/201105_1_44News.html |title=Egosoft MD Showcases ''X Rebirth'' at FedCon XX |access-date=2016-12-10 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513102033/https://www.egosoft.com/x/xnews/201105_1_44News.html }}</ref>

== 追加下载内容 ==

Egosoft在2014年12月11日推出本作的第一个[[追加下载内容|追加下载包]]《T族前哨站》（{{lang-en|The Teladi Outpost}}），并将游戏版本号升至3.0。该追加下载内容包含了一系列修复和对原版游戏的改进，且只支持64位操作系统。<ref name="pcgamer">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/x-rebirth-30-and-free-teladi-outpost-dlc-are-now-on-steam/ |title=X Rebirth 3.0 and free Teladi Outpost DLC are now on Steam |website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |date=2014-12-12 |accessdate=2016-12-10 |archive-date=2020-11-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128024747/https://www.pcgamer.com/x-rebirth-30-and-free-teladi-outpost-dlc-are-now-on-steam/ }}</ref>

Egosoft在2016年2月25日推出本作的第二个[[追加下载内容|追加下载包]]《光之家园》（{{lang-en|Home of Light}}），并将游戏版本号升至4.0。<ref name="pcgamer2">{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/new-trailer-details-the-changes-in-x-rebirth-home-of-light-expansion/ |title=New trailer details the changes in X Rebirth: Home of Light expansion |website=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |date=2016-02-29 |accessdate=2016-12-10 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423075118/https://www.pcgamer.com/new-trailer-details-the-changes-in-x-rebirth-home-of-light-expansion/ }}</ref>
